 <a href="tel:+17029048923" class="inline-flex min-h-[48px] items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-gold-500/40 px-6 py-3 font-mono text-sm font-medium text-gold-500 transition-all hover:border-gold-500 hover:bg-gold-500/5">
